Write Chat Comment to File

The Code below will import a user input setting as well as a module to be used by a timer to post messages in chat. 

The "Request-Line" is used to gather the user input and add it to a file of your choice (you will need to point this to the file you want to add to.)

The Request Module is setup to be a Bot Timer that will post a message in chat explaining to your viewers that they can use the !request "you text here" command to send requests in.

These 2 settings can be used in any combination to gather text input from users in chat.





